@workerUrl = http://localhost:8001
@ttsUrl     = http://localhost:8000

### Health check — worker .NET
GET {{workerUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check — TTS Python
GET {{ttsUrl}}/voices
Accept: application/json

###

### Enviar campaña (multipart — requiere un archivo .xlsx real)
# En VS Code con REST Client: cambia la ruta al xlsx que tengas
POST {{workerUrl}}/campaigns
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="client_id"

cliente01
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="voice"

es_MX-claude-high
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="phone_column"

telefono
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="text_column"

Message
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./test_campaign.xlsx
------Boundary--

###

### Ver estado de un job (reemplaza JOB_ID)
# @name status
GET {{workerUrl}}/campaigns/JOB_ID
Accept: application/json

###

### Ver todos los jobs en memoria
GET {{workerUrl}}/campaigns
Accept: application/json

###

### Prueba directa al endpoint JSON del TTS (sin pasar por el worker)
POST {{ttsUrl}}/v1/batch/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "job_directo_01",
  "clientId": "cliente01",
  "voiceName": "es_MX-claude-high",
  "pendingAudio": [
    { "recipient": "5512345678", "text": "Hola Juan, su pago vence manana." },
    { "recipient": "5598765432", "text": "Hola Maria, su factura esta disponible." }
  ]
}

###

### Recuperar manifiesto (reemplaza JOB_ID)
GET {{ttsUrl}}/v1/batch/cliente01/JOB_ID/JOB_ID/manifest
Accept: application/json

###
